OL,8,Fcompany put forward an offer of 2.6
OL,9,Fweeks' worth of pay every year of an
OL,10,Femployee's service. That means all
OL,11,Ffull-time staff who lose their job at
OL,12,Fthe Port Talbot plant will receive at
OL,13,Fleast #12,500.
